			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="A  node that plays when the player tries to click on a praying kuotoa. They will either praise you as the Chosen of their madeup god, or make you a new made-up god.&#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;BOOOAL - Booh-AL&#xD;&#xA;Mahkloompah - mak-LOOM-pah" />
